🔗
Link to a wallet: Will bind your wallet-id to this discord.
If on multiple discords, others don't have access to your possessed amount of eGLD
You can find this on the Maiar APP in **Profile > Settings > Privacy**
`egld$set | egld$join | egld$link` `<wallet_id>`

🔗🔗
Link / Unlink all wallets accross all servers
`me$set | me$join | me$link` `<wallet_id>`
`me$delete | me$remove`

❌
Unlink a wallet: Will remove your wallet-id from the current discord
`egld$unset | egld$delete | egld$unlink`

💹
Display: Will show current value of eGLD or/and with your amount
`egld$value`
`egld$wallet`

Server display: Will show all discord members' wallets
`egld$wallets`

⁉
Displays this :)
`egld$help`: utils.help,